Published on Jun 19, 2012 by adrianholovaty

Here's a medley of two melodies from the original Legend of Zelda NES game: the main theme and the "fairy fountain" theme. We funked it up a bit. :)

It was a great privilege to play with these guys. From left to right:
Adrian Holovaty, guitar
James Robbins, bass
Denis Chang, guitar

Check out Denis' instructional videos at http://www.dc-musicschool.com/ -- I've learned a TON from him over the years.

Recorded on June 16, 2012, at Django in June (http://www.djangoinjune.com/) in Northampton, MA.
